{"tid":1614382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（超實用）訂房小教學","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:57:51.000Z","uid":57616,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5cadda0ad86c21d0048ea562782dcfa7282cef","tid":1614382,"uid":57616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"依排酒店咁抵屌 相信大家最近都好想去訂酒店住返晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有以下小小既教學幫到大家（行內人）<br />\n<br />\n1）去酒店官網做會員 （例如：IHG 洲際集團）咁樣大家會享有98折既超抵優惠<br />\n<br />\n2）中學生既你未擁有信用卡 擔心訂唔到房？<br />\n唔緊要 依家用依張信用卡去訂 一定訂到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5413 5413 5413 5413 exp 10/21 （如你有更好既號碼組合 歡迎提供）<br />\n<br />\n3)唔需要擔心你既預訂被取消 根據IHG預訂policy 佢地唔會無情情斬左你隻booking 因為你係尊貴既會員<br />\n<br />\n4）一日過百隻no show 不是夢 （聽講酒店怕No show 影響forecast)<br />\n<br />\nPs. 你亦可以去各大OTA訂 總有一個適合你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bb26d2b28c9e008dd032d1f37a71854e91f039","tid":1614382,"uid":57616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:35:00.000Z","msg":"好實用架 推下啦～"},{"pid":"8818488b733f66bcdadec4a0aaf3018d7c84c6f4","tid":1614382,"uid":57616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"Push~"},{"pid":"d5b9e88031c03107a5d0e5ba5194f81b15283d8b","tid":1614382,"uid":57616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"無人理我 你地會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de03002ec61a55f11d1fac7f38712e99bfe6a73","tid":1614382,"uid":183051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"154fca864a1f2995fbe6e92b0901b2afe67f0c30","tid":1614382,"uid":107488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:58.000Z","msg":"推 受教"},{"pid":"28199eae74ab95d2b791e1ac593872eef466082b","tid":1614382,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB